name: FunkyBeefs disc golf towels Waffle Towel
description:
#2. 16"x24" Premium Microfiber Waffle Weave Towel is a HEAVY towel specifically designed for drying. It*s the heaviest towel we carry currently in terms of grams per square meter (440 GSM). These lint free microfiber towels are made up of hundreds of thousands of split fibers which allow the cloths to absorb up to seven times their own weight in liquid. The high-low construction allows liquid to be picked up in the high sections and then it wicks away to the lower sections which leaves a dryer surface of the towel. This means you can dry longer with the same towel. This heavy weight waffle towel is constructed from woven polyester / polyamide blend microfiber. The edges of the towels are sewn with over lock stitching. The corners of the towels are rounded which increases the life of the towel. When cared for properly our Microfiber Waffle Towel can last hundreds of washings. It's important to follow microfiber washing instructions closely; failure to care for them properly especially drying the towels with high heat can damage the towels and increase the risk of the towels scratching painted surfaces. 
Our Premium Microfiber Waffle Weave Towel is best used as a drying towel. The design of the towel makes it great at soaking up liquid and then releasing it when wrung out by hand. This makes it ideal for drying Frisbee disc, golf clubs, cars, trucks, motorcycles, boats and RV's. 
Video Review on side bar to the right.

name: FunkyBeefs Disc Golf Towels Plush Microfiber
description:
#3. The third towels are a 14"x14" Ultra Plush Microfiber Towel is among the highest quality Disc towels on the market. It's extremely plush and super soft. This two sided towel features one side of ultra plush microfiber material and a second side of shammy material. These terry type microfiber towels are made up of hundreds of thousands of split fibers which allow the cloths to clean aggressively without being abrasive. They are safe to use on windows, smooth and coarse surfaces as well as automotive finishes. Our 14"x14" Ultra Plush Microfiber Towels are constructed from woven polyester / polyamide blend microfiber. The open spaces in the fibers created by the splitting process are what give the towels its ability to hold dust, dirt, and excess wax and sealers. It also gives the cloth its ability to absorb and hold liquid. When cared for properly our 14"x14"Ultra Plush Microfiber Towel can last hundreds of washings.
Video Review on the side bar to the right
